{{Documentation subpage}}
== Usage ==
'''Month:'''{{plainlist|
*{{tlg|Last month (short)|alttext=Lmonth}} produces {{Lmonth}}
*{{tlg|Next month (short)|alttext=Nmonth}} produces {{Nmonth}}
*{{tl|Last month}} produces {{Last month}}
*{{tl|This month}} produces {{This month}}
*{{tl|Next month}} produces {{Next month}}
}}
== See also ==
*{{tl|Calendar}}
*{{tl|Calendar clock with Wikipedia stats}}
*{{tl|Clock}}
